...apakah dia sudah melalui...

00:10:19.068 --> 00:10:21.106
...untuk mencapai sini.'

00:10:22.003 --> 00:10:23.257
'Ini...

00:10:24.653 --> 00:10:27.681
...gelar bukanlah
